{"tid":102184,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[後悔] 入左紅磚電機，連參加比賽既資格都無","createTime":"2017-01-31T12:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T12:35:05.000Z","uid":14170,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2d9f0c3349687c97ce8ad45d390f696b90def9f","tid":102184,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/31/202331_2a6e2c716e6d9e6caeb937c71d57a10e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F31%2F202331_2a6e2c716e6d9e6caeb937c71d57a10e.jpg&h=b7745a1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明我 IVE GPA 3.6，果陣中大科大工程都收我，但係我聽班垃圾高登仔吹捧理大電機，然後班呀蛇又話三大既電子乞食點點點，結果我棄中科取理大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知今年理大電機有成 100 人，Part time 果邊又幾十個，最慘 HKU 電機電子又 80個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以搵工我都打定輸數，因為兩電一鐵夾埋每年只請 40 人左右，剩係港大仔圍內都爭崩頭，我諗住轉行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n於是搵到呢個比賽，點知理大連參加比賽既資格都無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好後悔揀左理大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6097c0ab75caa5122d57fbe2efcd2d97ac994677","tid":102184,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:33:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b72849dd96ac2dd9b31dedcf209be03129bb745","tid":102184,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:37:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩比賽</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://jpmc.recsolucampus.com/candidatepreferenceform.php?formId=ZWNm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjpmc.recsolucampus.com%2Fcandidatepreferenceform.php%3FformId%3DZWNm&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=e9e29025\" target=\"_blank\">https://jpmc.recsolucampus.com/candidatepreferenceform.php?formId=ZWNm</a>"},{"pid":"0